name: ONIMATA - VOL.02
description:
VOL.02 "IN THE VOID"

O-01 has fallen to the void completely. A dark, and empty place where it almost feels like there's no way out of there. As O-01 walk further, there's someone waiting for him.

It is O-03, a best friend that never left. Stepping out from the shadow there to make O-01 realise that this is just an illusion. O-01 asked him to leave him alone but O-03 resisting and prepare himself to fight O-01 at all cost to save him. What's happening here? Who would win?
